flowchart TD
    A[User Starts Training] --> B[Authorization Check]
    B --> C{Authorized?}
    C -->|No| D[Reject Request<br/>403 Forbidden]
    C -->|Yes| E[Project Source Validation]

    E --> F{Git Clone or ZIP Valid?}
    F -->|No| G[Job Not Started<br/>Notify User]
    F -->|Yes| H[Disk Capacity Check]

    H --> I{Free Disk >= 5GB?}
    I -->|No| J[Job Not Started<br/>Status FAILED<br/>Notify User]
    I -->|Yes| K[Queue Job]

    K --> L[Launch Docker Container]
    L --> M{Container Starts?}
    M -->|No| N[Status FAILED<br/>Capture Runner Error]
    M -->|Yes| O[Stream stdout / stderr]

    O --> P{Training Result}
    P -->|Exit Code 0| Q[Status SUCCESS]
    P -->|Non-zero Exit| R[Status FAILED<br/>Persist Error Logs]
    P -->|User Cancel| S[Status CANCELLED<br/>Stop Container]
    P -->|Server Restart| T[Status RETRYING<br/>Requeue Job]

    Q --> U[Register Artifacts]
    U --> V{Artifact Registration OK?}
    V -->|No| W[Artifact Status FAILED<br/>Training Remains SUCCESS<br/>Notify User]
    V -->|Yes| X[Create Model Version]

    R --> Y[Send Failure Email]
    N --> Y
    W --> Z[In-App Notification]
    X --> AA[Send Success Email]
    T --> K
